sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Framework as MultipeerConnectivity

  box MultipeerActor
    participant MPActor as MultipeerActor
    participant PeerMap as peerMap
  end

  participant Client as MultipeerClient
  participant Reducers as TCA Reducers

  Framework->>MPActor: discovered(MCPeerID)
  MPActor->>PeerMap: peerMap[mcPeer] = Peer(...)
  Note over MPActor,PeerMap: MCPeerID is contained inside actor

  MPActor-->>Client: MultipeerEvent.peerDiscovered(Peer)
  Client-->>Reducers: events() emits .peerDiscovered(Peer)
